Pro-worker AI is all about using artificial intelligence to complement human abilities. It enhances what professionals can do, helping them tackle more complex tasks and boost productivity. It’s about AI working alongside people, allowing them to focus on higher-value work, improving job satisfaction, and creating a future where both humans and technology thrive together. 

By embracing opportunities to learn more about AI and machine learning, such as through online programs, you can enhance your skills and position yourself for success in this evolving landscape. To explore AI programs offered by Emeritus, click the link in the bio or visit https://emrt.us/ig-aiml
